2013年3月，曼德斯表示他不会回归执导系列的下一部电影《邦德24》<ref name="noMendes" /><ref name="EmpireMendes" />，但他后来撤回这一说法，宣布回归並称找到了剧本，还为系列的长期发展作了规划<ref>{{cite news|title=''Spectre'': Sam Mendes hints at 'more mischief' in new James Bond film|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30328726|first=Lizo|last=Mzimba|work=bbc.co.uk|publisher=BBC|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205135013/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30328726|archive-date=2014-12-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于导演《[[007：空降危機|空降危機]]》和《鬼影帝國》，曼德斯成为自[[约翰·葛伦_(导演)|约翰·葛伦]]导演1987年电影《[[黎明生机|黎明生机]]》和1989年电影《[[杀人执照|杀人执照]]》以来，首位连续监制两部邦德电影的导演。《[[007：空降危機|空降危機]]》编剧[[约翰·罗根|约翰·罗根]]继续担任编剧<ref name="MendesLogan to return" />，伴随他的是六部为邦德电影编剧的[[尼尔·珀维斯|尼尔·珀维斯]]和[[罗伯特·韦德|罗伯特·韦德]]（{{lang|en|Neal Purvis and Robert Wade}}）<ref name=zetumer>{{cite news |title=A James Bond Set Visit and Seven Exclusive Quantum of Solace Images! |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |date=2008-04-04 |url=http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/quantum_of_solace/news/1719930/a_james_bond_set_visit_and_seven_exclusive_quantum_of_solace_images |accessdate=2014-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081005195337/http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/quantum_of_solace/news/1719930/a_james_bond_set_visit_and_seven_exclusive_quantum_of_solace_images |archivedate=2008-10-05 }}</ref>。编剧[[杰斯·巴特沃斯|杰斯·巴特沃斯]]、曼德斯和克雷格也参与剧本创作<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brockes|first1=Emma|title=All or Nothing|url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/11/10/nothing-2|accessdate=2014-12-16|work=The New Yorker|date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217004515/http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2014/11/10/nothing-2|archive-date=2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[丹尼斯·加斯纳|丹尼斯·加斯纳]]（{{lang|en|Dennis Gassner}}）回归担任影片艺术指导，而摄影师[[霍伊特·冯·霍特玛|霍伊特·冯·霍特玛]]将接替[[罗杰·迪金斯|罗杰·迪金斯]]<ref name="cast & crew">{{cite news|url=http://www.007.com/bond-returns-in-spectre/|title=Bond returns in ''Spectre''|work=007.com|publisher=Eon Productions|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716222443/http://www.007.com/bond-returns-in-spectre/|archive-date=2015-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="hvh">{{cite web |last1=Tapley |first1=Kristopher |title=Interstellar cinematographer on grounding Nolan's movie and shooting Bond on film |url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/interstellar-cinematographer-on-grounding-nolans-movie-and-shooting-bond-on-film/single-page |website=HitFix |accessdate=2014-12-04 |date=2014-11-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722044553/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/interstellar-cinematographer-on-grounding-nolans-movie-and-shooting-bond-on-film/single-page |archivedate=2015-07-22 }}</ref>。2015年7月，曼德斯表示影片剧组人数高达一千人名，比《[[007：空降危機|空降危機]]》要多。克雷格被列为联合制片人<ref name="mendes NSNA">{{cite web|title=Never Say Never Again (Again)|url=https://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-180715-sam-mendes-interview?t=&s=&id=03930|date=2015-07-16|accessdate=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722070348/https://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-180715-sam-mendes-interview?t=&s=&id=03930|archive-date=2015-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 摄制 ===
导演[[山姆·曼德斯|山姆·曼德斯]]透露，影片将于2014年12月8日在[[松林制片厂|松林制片厂]]开机，拍摄持续7个月<ref>{{cite web|last1=Miller|first1=Ross|title=The next James Bond film is called Spectre: new car, poster, and full cast confirmed|url=http://www.theverge.com/2014/12/4/7327013/james-bond-24-full-cast-title-car-release-date|website=The Verge|accessdate=2014-12-04|date=2014-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209092435/http://www.theverge.com/2014/12/4/7327013/james-bond-24-full-cast-title-car-release-date|archive-date=2014-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼德斯证实了数处取景地，包括[[伦敦|伦敦]]、[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]、[[罗马|罗马]]、[[丹吉尔|丹吉尔]]、[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]][[伊尔福德|伊尔福德]]、[[索尔登|索尔登]]、[[上蒂利拉赫|上蒂利拉赫]]和[[奥地利|奥地利]]的[[阿尔陶塞|阿尔陶塞]]<ref>{{cite web|url = https://twitter.com/007/status/540461455955742720|title = James Bond|date = 2014-12-04|accessdate = 2014-12-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160128114506/https://twitter.com/007/status/540461455955742720|archive-date = 2016-01-28|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="#2">{{cite web|title=James Bond 24: new 007 film title unveiled as 'Spectre' with Christoph Waltz confirmed as Bond villain|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/james-bond-new-007-film-details-to-be-announced-live-from-pinewood-studios-9902204.html|publisher=standard.co.uk|accessdate=2014-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141204145516/http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/james-bond-new-007-film-details-to-be-announced-live-from-pinewood-studios-9902204.html|archive-date=2014-12-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。摄影师[[霍伊特·范·霍特玛|霍伊特·范·霍特玛]]将采用[[柯达|柯达]]胶卷拍摄<ref>{{cite web|title=Productions on Kodak Motion Picture Film|url=http://www.motion.kodak.com/motion/Customers/Productions/index.htm|website=Kodak|accessdate=2014-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208230814/http://www.motion.kodak.com/motion/Customers/Productions/index.htm|archive-date=2014-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Tapley |first1=Kristopher |title=Interstellar cinematographer on grounding Nolan's movie and shooting Bond on film |url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/interstellar-cinematographer-on-grounding-nolans-movie-and-shooting-bond-on-film/single-page |website=HitFix |accessdate=2014-12-04 |date=2014-12-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722044553/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/interstellar-cinematographer-on-grounding-nolans-movie-and-shooting-bond-on-film/single-page |archivedate=2015-07-22 }}</ref>。早期取景地包括松林制片厂和伦敦郊区。克雷格与哈里斯在邦德的住宅拍了很多场景，还与金尼尔在泰晤士河下开船<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond23-gallery-london-filming-december15?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03809|title=London Filming (1)|work=MI6-HQ.COM|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402195239/http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond23-gallery-london-filming-december15?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03809|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片于2014年12月在[[奥地利|奥地利]]开机，取景地包括[[索尔登|索尔登]]（{{lang|de|Sölden}}）的奥茨山谷冰川路（{{lang|de|Ötztal Glacier Road}}）、拉滕贝格冰川（{{lang|de|Rettenbach}}）及临近的滑雪场和缆车站、[[上帝利拉赫|上帝利拉赫]]和[[阿尔陶塞湖|阿尔陶塞湖]]，2015年2月结束<ref>{{cite web|url= https://twitter.com/007/status/540461455955742720|title= James Bond|date= 2014-12-04|accessdate= 2014-12-04|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160128114506/https://twitter.com/007/status/540461455955742720|archive-date= 2016-01-28|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="#2"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Sölden – filming location for the new James Bond Movie|url=http://www.soelden.com/james-bond-007-en|first1=Jakob|last1=Falkner|first2=Oliver|last2=Swartz|work=soelden.com|date=2014-12-05|accessdate=2014-12-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208180346/http://www.soelden.com/james-bond-007-en|archivedate=2014-12-08}}</ref>。奥地利市中心的取景地包括[[阿尔卑斯山|阿尔卑斯山]]的冰Q餐厅（{{lang|de|Ice Q Restaurant}}），在片中它是虚构的私人诊所霍福乐诊所（{{lang|de|Hoffler Klinik}}）。动作场景中出现了[[路虎卫士|路虎卫士大脚怪版]]（{{lang|en|Land Rover Defender Bigfoot}}）和[[路虎揽胜运动版|路虎揽胜运动版]]（{{lang|en|Range Rover Sport}}）<ref name="cx75">{{cite web|title=Jaguar and Land Rover Announce Partnership with Spectre the 24th James Bond Adventure|url=http://www.jaguar.com/news/jlr-james-bond-partnership.html|accessdate=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213075744/http://www.jaguar.com/news/jlr-james-bond-partnership.html|archive-date=2015-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。制作因克雷格在拍摄打斗场面时扭伤膝盖而被暂停<ref>{{cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Daniel Craig Returns To ''Spectre'' Today After Knee Injury Earlier This Week|url=http://deadline.com/2015/02/daniel-craig-returns-to-spectre-today-after-knee-injury-earlier-this-week-1201368678/|website=deadline.com|publisher=Deadline|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210071916/http://deadline.com/2015/02/daniel-craig-returns-to-spectre-today-after-knee-injury-earlier-this-week-1201368678/|archive-date=2015-02-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后来的一起车祸事故有三名剧组成员受伤，其中至少一人伤势严重<ref>{{cite web|title=3 Injured during filming of new Bond flick in Austria|url=http://www.efe.com/efe/noticias/english/varios/injured-during-filming-new-bond-flick-austria/4/40822/2542386|website=efe.com|publisher=EFE|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402150805/http://www.efe.com/efe/noticias/english/varios/injured-during-filming-new-bond-flick-austria/4/40822/2542386|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Agence France Press|title=Two technicians seriously injured on James Bond set in Austria|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/life-style/entertainment/2015/02/18/Two-technicians-seriously-injured-on-James-Bond-set-in-Austria-.html|website=alarabiya.net|publisher=Al Arabiya|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150306224201/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/life-style/entertainment/2015/02/18/Two-technicians-seriously-injured-on-James-Bond-set-in-Austria-.html|archive-date=2015-03-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

