剧组暂时返回英国，在[[牛津郡|牛津郡]]的[[布伦海姆宫|布伦海姆宫]]拍摄，在片中它是[[罗马|罗马]]的景点<ref>{{cite news|last=Jackson|first=Marc|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2949636/Bond-heads-Blenheim-Palace-Spectre-shoot.html|title=Your car is ready, Mr Bond: 007's most famous rides are lined up outside Winston Churchill's birthplace Blenheim Palace as Spectre shoot returns to UK|publisher=''Daily Mail''|date=2015-02-11|accessdate=2015-09-13|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150921140252/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2949636/Bond-heads-Blenheim-Palace-Spectre-shoot.html|archive-date=2015-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后剧组跨越整个[[罗马|罗马]]进行为期五个星期的拍摄，取景地包括[[西克斯图桥|西克斯图桥]]（{{lang|en|Ponte Sisto}}）和[[古罗马广场|古罗马广场]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.007.com/spectre-moves-to-rome/|title=''Spectre'' moves to Rome|work=007.com|publisher=Danjaq LLC|accessdate=2015-03-02|date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qA3alBpa?url=http://www.007.com/spectre-moves-to-rome/|archive-date=2017-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。制作面临着各种特殊利益集团和市政当局的反对，他们担心会可能损害到城里的历史建筑及制作中出现的涂鸦和垃圾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-20150219-rome-filming-day1?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03852|title=Rome Filming (1)|work=MI6-HQ.COM|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402184911/http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-20150219-rome-filming-day1?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03852|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-20150109-rome-car-chase-quattro-fontane?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03828|title=Arrivederci Mr. Bond|work=MI6-HQ.COM|access-date=2015-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402220846/http://www.mi6-hq.com/sections/articles/bond-24-report-20150109-rome-car-chase-quattro-fontane?t=&s=mi6_update&id=03828|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。追车场面的拍摄沿着[[台伯河|台伯河]]穿过罗马的大街小巷，[[阿斯顿·马丁DB10|阿斯顿·马丁DB10]]和[[捷豹C-X75|捷豹C-X75]]登场<ref name="cx75"/>。C-X75原本作为混合动力电动车被开发，带有四独立电池驱动引擎，但开发项目被取消<ref name=MT092810>{{cite news|url=http://www.motortrend.com/auto_shows/paris/2010/1009_jaguar_c_x75_concept/index.html|title=First Look: Jaguar C-X75 Concept|work=Motor Trend|date=2010-09-28|accessdate=2015-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811162630/http://www.motortrend.com/auto_shows/paris/2010/1009_jaguar_c_x75_concept/index.html|archive-date=2011-08-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但用于拍摄的版本被转换为用常规的内燃机驱动，以减少复杂混合动力系统机械问题有可能带来的破坏。用于拍戏的C-X75由为捷豹建造了C-X75原型的[[一级方程式赛车|一级方程式赛车]][[威廉姆斯车队|威廉姆斯车队]]工程部开发<ref>{{cite news|url=http://jalopnik.com/everything-you-havent-seen-yet-about-spectres-jaguar-c-1730568764?rev=1442255691259|title=Everything you haven't seen yet about ''Spectre''-{}-'s Jaguar C-X75 |work=jalopnik|accessdate=2015-09-15}}</ref>。

