[[罗马|罗马]]的拍摄完成后，三月下旬剧组转战[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]拍摄影片开头，[[宪法广场_(墨西哥城)|宪法广场]]和[[墨西哥城历史中心区|墨西哥城历史中心区]]的[[亡灵节|亡灵节]]场景被摄制<ref>{{cite web|title=James Bond se apodera del Centro Histórico|url=http://www.excelsior.com.mx/funcion/2015/03/17/1013869#imagen-2|website=Excelsion Newspaper Online|accessdate=2015-03-19|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320010859/http://www.excelsior.com.mx/funcion/2015/03/17/1013869#imagen-2|archive-date=2015-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。计划取景地需要封闭城市广场，修整多座建筑物预防损坏<ref>{{cite web|title=Inician Ensayos de escenas de Spectre en El Zocalo|url=http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/espectaculos/2015/inician-ensayos-de-escenas-de-39spectre-39-en-el-zocalo-1085857.html|website=Periodico El Universal|accessdate=2015-03-19|language=es|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321232222/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/espectaculos/2015/inician-ensayos-de-escenas-de-39spectre-39-en-el-zocalo-1085857.html|archive-date=2015-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，好让特技飞行员[[查克·亚伦|查克·亚伦]]（{{lang|en|Chuck Aaron}}）操作[[梅赛施密特-博尔科-布洛姆·博150直升机|梅赛施密特-博尔科-布洛姆·博150直升机]]（{{lang|en|Messerschmitt-Bölkow-Blohm Bo 150}}）。墨西哥媒体的报道补充道，第二单元剧组将移师[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]的[[帕伦克|帕伦克]]拍摄被认为在城市地区拍太过危险的空中回旋场景<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mexico.cnn.com/entretenimiento/2015/04/08/palenque-la-ultima-escala-de-james-bond-en-su-aventura-mexicana|title=Palenque, la última escala de James Bond en su aventura mexicana|publisher=''[[CNN|CNN]]''|date=2015-04-08|accessdate=2015-09-13|language=es|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002012500/http://mexico.cnn.com/entretenimiento/2015/04/08/palenque-la-ultima-escala-de-james-bond-en-su-aventura-mexicana|archivedate=2015-10-02}}</ref>。

墨西哥的拍摄结束后，剧组短暂休整，克雷格飞往[[纽约|纽约]]接受小手术解决膝伤。据报道，拍摄并未受到影响，他按计划于4月22日返回松林制片厂拍戏<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Craig has knee surgery after Bond injury|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-32189448|accessdate=2015-04-06|work=BBC News|date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406015333/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-32189448|archive-date=2015-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年4月18日，在伦敦[[倫敦市政廳_(南華克)|市政厅]]的简要拍摄中曼德斯出现<ref>{{cite news|title=James Bond director Sam Mendes shoots new Spectre scenes inside London's iconic City Hall as filming resumes after Daniel Craig's set injury|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3044905/James-Bond-director-Sam-Mendes-shoots-new-Spectre-scenes-inside-London-s-iconic-City-Hall-filming-resumes-Daniel-Craig-s-set-injury.html|accessdate=2015-05-19|work=Daily Mail|date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150524205427/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3044905/James-Bond-director-Sam-Mendes-shoots-new-Spectre-scenes-inside-London-s-iconic-City-Hall-filming-resumes-Daniel-Craig-s-set-injury.html|archive-date=2015-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月17日剧组在泰晤士河拍摄。在克雷格和乘坐快艇的赛杜出现的特技场面中，一架低空飞行的直升机于夜间在[[西敏桥|威斯敏斯特桥]]附近出现，为此威斯敏斯特桥和[[兰贝斯桥|兰贝斯桥]]被暂时关闭<ref>{{cite news|title=James Bond fans see filming of Spectre on River Thames in London|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-london-32777018|accessdate=2015-05-19|work=BBC News|date=2015-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520190847/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-london-32777018|archive-date=2015-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。场景也在沃克斯豪尔十字路口靠近[[军情六处总部|军情六处总部]]的河流进行<ref name=BBCMay15>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-32777018|title=James Bond fans see filming of Spectre on River Thames in London|date=2015-05-18|work=BBC News Online|accessdate=2015-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521005934/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-32777018|archive-date=2015-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在威斯敏斯特桥的简单取景完成一周后，剧组回到这条河。[[伦敦消防队|伦敦消防队]]（{{lang|en|London Fire Brigade}}）为场景模拟降水，监测用于拍摄的烟雾。克雷格、赛杜、瓦尔兹、哈里斯、费因斯出现在片场<ref>{{cite news|title=Spectre attacks Big Ben as James Bond returns to do battle with old enemy|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/spectre-attacks-big-ben-james-5752224|accessdate=2015-05-24|work=Mirror|date=2015-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525000355/http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/spectre-attacks-big-ben-james-5752224|archive-date=2015-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前，费因斯被枪杀的场景在[[科文特花园|科文特花园]]的一座餐厅拍摄<ref>{{cite news|title=Spectre filming at Rules restaurant in London|url=http://www.jamesbondlifestyle.com/news/spectre-filming-rules-restaurant-london|accessdate=2015-05-24|work=James Bond Lifestyle|date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524214342/http://www.jamesbondlifestyle.com/news/spectre-filming-rules-restaurant-london|archive-date=2015-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。剧组随后转战[[特拉法加广场|特拉法加广场]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Daniel Craig brings London to a standstill as he shoots scenes for new Bond film Spectre at capital's famous landmarks|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3105139/Daniel-Craig-brings-London-standstill-shoots-scenes-new-Bond-film-Spectre-capital-s-famous-landmarks.html|accessdate=2015-06-08|work=Daily Mail|date=2015-06-01|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150614135721/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3105139/Daniel-Craig-brings-London-standstill-shoots-scenes-new-Bond-film-Spectre-capital-s-famous-landmarks.html|archive-date=2015-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。六月初，克雷格、赛杜和瓦尔兹等剧组成员回到泰晤士河最后一次继续此前在河中进行的拍摄<ref>{{cite news|title=James Bond villain Christoph Waltz gets the CGI treatment as he is spotted with white capture dots on his face as he films scenes for Spectre in London|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3114929/Bond-villain-Christoph-Waltz-spotted-time-set-Spectre-new-007-film-shoots-action-packed-scenes-London.html|accessdate=2015-06-08|work=Daily Mail|date=2015-06-08|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150614135656/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3114929/Bond-villain-Christoph-Waltz-spotted-time-set-Spectre-new-007-film-shoots-action-packed-scenes-London.html|archive-date=2015-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

结束英国的摄制后，剧组六月份转战[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]，第二单元剧组完成前期工作后，在[[乌季达|乌季达]]、[[丹吉尔|丹吉尔]]和[[伊尔福德|伊尔福德]]进行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2014/artisans/news/spectre-king-tut-and-the-book-of-the-dead-sail-to-morocco-1201372107/|title='Spectre', 'King Tut' and 'The Book of the Dead' Sail To Morocco|date=2014-12-06|accessdate=2015-02-27|work=variety.com/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315173521/http://variety.com/2014/artisans/news/spectre-king-tut-and-the-book-of-the-dead-sail-to-morocco-1201372107/|archive-date=2015-03-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

