[[汤玛斯·纽曼|汤玛斯·纽曼]]回归担任本片配乐<ref name="cast & crew"/>。与以往影片一旦转入后期制作阶段就创作配乐的模式不同，纽曼在摄制期间已着手创作<ref name="delve deep"/>。2015年7月发布的剧场版预告片包含[[约翰·巴瑞|约翰·巴瑞]]的《[[女王密使|女王密使]]》主题曲是Sam Smith的Writing's On The Wall<ref name="OHMSS sample">{{cite web|title=New Spectre Trailer|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTDaET-JweU|website=You Tube|accessdate=2015-07-30|date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150729180830/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LTDaET-JweU|archive-date=2015-07-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Trailer soundtrack">{{cite web|last1=Ross|first1=Daniel|title=New Bond soundtrack: what does the new Spectre trailer tell us?|url=http://www.classicfm.com/composers/newman/news/james-bond-spectre-soundtrack/#QEke7FmlEbKd4XIp.97|website=Classic FM|accessdate=2015-07-30|date=2015-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801234554/http://www.classicfm.com/composers/newman/news/james-bond-spectre-soundtrack/#QEke7FmlEbKd4XIp.97|archive-date=2015-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。曼德斯透露称成片的音乐长达100多分钟<ref name="mendes NSNA"/>。

