2015年3月，影片首支预告片全球发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.007.com/watch-the-spectre-teaser-trailer/|title=Watch the ''Spectre Teaser Trailer|work=The Official James Bond 007 Website|accessdate=2015-05-19|date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qA3nqjJG?url=http://www.007.com/watch-the-spectre-teaser-trailer/|archive-date=2017-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，电视宣传片于6月份[[2015年NBA总决赛|NBA总决赛]]发布<ref>{{cite web|title=《007:幽灵党》首曝电视宣传片 邦德狂奔飙车玩命探案 与蕾雅赛杜上演亲密戏份|url=http://news.mtime.com/2015/06/10/1543499.html|website=Mtime时光网|accessdate=2015-10-01|date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003040654/http://news.mtime.com/2015/06/10/1543499.html|archive-date=2015-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，剧场版预告片7月发布<ref name="21 Jul trailer">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jul/22/spectre-trailer-watch-the-first-full-length-trailer-for-the-new-james-bond-film|title=''Spectre'' trailer: watch the first full-length trailer for the new James Bond film|work=The Guardian|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2015-07-21|accessdate=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722164051/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jul/22/spectre-trailer-watch-the-first-full-length-trailer-for-the-new-james-bond-film|archive-date=2015-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
影片全球首映礼将于2015年10月26日举行，同日影片将在[[英国|英国]]和[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]正式上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/london-lands-spectre-world-premiere-809422|title=London Lands ''Spectre'' World Premiere|first=Alex|last=Ritman|work=The Hollywood Reporter|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)|date=2015-07-17|accessdate=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719182709/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/london-lands-spectre-world-premiere-809422|archive-date=2015-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年11月6日全球上映<ref name="mendes on spectre">{{cite web|title=Sam Mendes on Spectre|url=http://www.007.com/sam-mendes-on-spectre/|website=007.com|publisher=Eon Productions|accessdate=2015-02-26|date=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qA3jVnIw?url=http://www.007.com/sam-mendes-on-spectre/|archive-date=2017-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。开机消息公布后，[[派拉蒙影业|派拉蒙影业]]提前了《[[碟中谍5：神秘国度|碟中谍5：神秘国度]]》的档期，避免与影片正面交锋<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paramount-shifts-mission-impossible-5-767313?utm_source=Sailthru&utm_medium=email&utm_term=hollywoodreporter_breakingnews&utm_campaign=THR%20Breaking%20News_now_2015-01-26%2012:53:42_ehayden/|title=Paramount Shifts 'Mission: Impossible 5' Release Date to Summer 2015|first1=Erik|last1=Hayden|first2=Pamela|last2=McClintock|publisher=''[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|date=2015-01-26|accessdate=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412122116/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paramount-shifts-mission-impossible-5-767313?utm_source=Sailthru&utm_medium=email&utm_term=hollywoodreporter_breakingnews&utm_campaign=THR%20Breaking%20News_now_2015-01-26%2012%3A53%3A42_ehayden%2F|archive-date=2015-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月，伴随着《[[007：空降危機|空降危機]]》给公司带来的成功，[[IMAX|IMAX]]宣布影片将旗下电影院将放映影片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=11712&catid=110&t=mi6&s=bond24|title='SPECTRE' to be shown in IMAX around the world|work=Mi6-HQ|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614024043/https://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=11712&catid=110&t=mi6&s=bond24|archive-date=2015-06-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據367篇專業影評持有63%的新鮮度，平均得分6.40／10；該網站共識：「《007：惡魔四伏》的動力幾乎達到[[丹尼爾·克雷格|丹尼爾·克雷格]]的重啟龐德更接近於早期作品的輝煌，雖然不可否認這依賴於007建立的公式」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spectre_2015/|title=Spectre (2015)|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028050928/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spectre_2015|archive-date=2016-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分60，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分6.8，好壞平均參雜<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/spectre |title=Spectre |work=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106013751/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/spectre |archive-date=2015-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影評人稱讚其開場戲、動作場面、特技和攝影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/reviews-recommendations/film-week-spectre |title=Film of the week: SPECTRE |work=BFI |accessdate=2015-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030032903/http://www.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/reviews-recommendations/film-week-spectre |archive-date=2015-10-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
电影全球票房8.807亿美元（除特别说明，下同），其中英国市场占1.355亿，北美占2.001亿<ref name=BOM />。从全球上看，影片是继《[[007：大破天幕杀机|天幕杀机]]》后票房第二高的《[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德]]》电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=jamesbond.htm|title=James Bond|work=''Box Office Mojo''|accessdate=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140621071011/http://boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=jamesbond.htm|archive-date=2014-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是[[2015年电影列表|2015年票房第六高的电影]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2015|title=2015 worldwide grosses|work=''Box Office Mojo''|accessdate=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513173308/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2015|archive-date=2016-05-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]计算，把电影制片费用和收益计算在内，毛利润为9840万美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/spectre-profit-box-office-2015-james-bond-1201723528/|title=No. 16 'Spectre' – 2015 Most Valuable Movie Blockbuster Tournament|author=Mike Fleming Jr|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2016-03-21|accessdate=2016-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323041610/http://deadline.com/2016/03/spectre-profit-box-office-2015-james-bond-1201723528/|archive-date=2016-03-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在英国，电影周一点映票房410万英镑（640万）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/spectre-uk-box-office-opening-1201595185/ |title='Spectre' Shakes UK Box Office With $6.4M In Monday Previews |publisher=Deadline.com |access-date=2015-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028225500/http://deadline.com/2015/10/spectre-uk-box-office-opening-1201595185/ |archive-date=2015-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首映当日票房630万英镑（920万）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/spectre-uk-box-office-opening-1201595185/|title=''Spectre'' Sets UK Box Office Record With $9.2M On Day Two|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-10-28|accessdate=2015-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028225500/http://deadline.com/2015/10/spectre-uk-box-office-opening-1201595185/|archive-date=2015-10-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后于星期三入账570万英镑（880万）,两日都创下英国票房纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/spectre-box-office-james-bond-1201629856/|title=Box Office: ''Spectre'' Breaks Wednesday Record in U.K.|author=Brent Lang|work=Variety|date=2015-10-29|accessdate=2015-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029214204/http://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/spectre-box-office-james-bond-1201629856/|archive-date=2015-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首周票房4170万英镑（6380万），打破由《[[哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯_(電影)|哈利波特：阿茲卡班的逃犯]]》在2004年创下的2.388亿英镑（3.69亿）的英国上映首周最高纪录<ref>{{cite web|title=''Spectre breaks UK Box Office Records: The biggest UK opening of all time|url=http://www.007.com/spectre-breaks-box-office-records/|publisher=007|date=2015-11-02|accessdate=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qA3woOop?url=http://www.007.com/spectre-breaks-box-office-records/|archive-date=2017-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。周末票房2040万英镑（3120万），击败前作的2010万英镑（3100万）。影片还凭借11万美元每块屏幕首映收益击败10.2万的《[[黑暗骑士|黑暗骑士]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-box-office-record-opening-uk-1201601884/|title=''Spectre'' Smashes Records With $80.4M Opening|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-01|accessdate=2015-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103154245/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-box-office-record-opening-uk-1201601884/|archive-date=2015-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而北美首映总收益为1.363亿<ref name="Overseas17thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-good-dinosaur-martian-china-international-box-office-results-1201645755/|title='Mockingjay' Rules Roost; 'Good Dinosaur' Hatches With $29M; 'The Martian' Lands $50M In China – Intl Box Office|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-29|accessdate=2015-11-30|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qEsAFIlf?url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-good-dinosaur-martian-china-international-box-office-results-1201645755/|archive-date=2017-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在英国，影片凭借1009万超越《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》，成为该国票房最高的IMAX电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/uk-box-office-hunger-games-843123|title=U.K. Box Office: Final 'Hunger Games' on Top, 'Spectre' Sets Imax Record|author=Alex Ritman|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-11-23|accessdate=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qEsd69Jo?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/uk-box-office-hunger-games-843123|archive-date=2017-05-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

包括点映在内，影片在德国、澳大利亚和韩国首映票房分别为2245万、870万和820万<ref name="Overseas15thOpening"/>，其中德国创下该国周六史上最高的票房纪录<ref name="Day2">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-james-bond-peanuts-movie-snoopy-maze-runner-china-international-box-office-results-1201614437/|title='Spectre' No. 1 Everywhere It Has Opened, Pushes Gross To $290M – Intl B.O. Final|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117051106/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-james-bond-peanuts-movie-snoopy-maze-runner-china-international-box-office-results-1201614437/|archive-date=2015-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|11月13日巴黎袭击案]]导致众多影业关门，影片在法国还是以1460万（包括点映的200万）开画<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paris-attacks-spectre-prevails-france-840427|title=Paris Attacks: 'Spectre' Prevails in France Despite Cinema Closures|author=Pamela McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116101244/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/paris-attacks-spectre-prevails-france-840427|archive-date=2015-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在影片取景地之一的墨西哥，影片以前作两倍多的4500万成绩首秀<ref name="Day2"/>。影片还击败前作北欧地区票房，其中芬兰266万、挪威291万<ref name="Day1">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-box-office-record-opening-uk-1201601884/|title='Spectre' Smashes Records With $80.12M Opening; Bond Bow Breaks 'Skyfall'|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-01|access-date=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151103154245/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-box-office-record-opening-uk-1201601884/|archive-date=2015-11-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>、丹麦420万、荷兰338万、瑞典310万<ref name="Day1"/>。在印度，影片开画时凭借480万登顶，比前作多4%<ref name="Overseas16thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-spectre-international-box-office-results-1201634041/|title='Mockingjay' Lands At $144.5M As China & Caution In Europe Squeeze Hwd – Intl B.O. Final|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-24|accessdate=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124224450/http://deadline.com/2015/11/hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-spectre-international-box-office-results-1201634041/|archive-date=2015-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该片占据瑞士德语区票房榜榜首长达四个星期，甚至在荷兰占据七个星期（《[[小黄人|小黄人]]》是当年该国最卖座的电影）<ref name="Overseas17thOpening"/><ref name="Overseas20thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/mockingjay-part-2-good-dinosaur-spectre-heart-of-the-sea-point-break-star-wars-international-box-office-results-1201666009/|title=Katniss Retakes No. 1 From China 'Surprise', 'Good Dinosaur' in 3rd, 'Sea', 007 Round Out Top 5 – Intl Box Office Final|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-12-13|accessdate=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214184946/http://deadline.com/2015/12/mockingjay-part-2-good-dinosaur-spectre-heart-of-the-sea-point-break-star-wars-international-box-office-results-1201666009/|archive-date=2015-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。票房榜榜首市场是德国（7030万）和法国（3880万）<ref name="Overseas1stOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/sherlock-star-wars-the-force-awakens-mojin-checco-zalone-international-box-office-results-1201675349/|title='Star Wars', Local-Language & Family Pics Lead; 'Sherlock' Shines In Korea – Intl B.O.|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2016-01-03|accessdate=2016-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160104182357/http://deadline.com/2016/01/sherlock-star-wars-the-force-awakens-mojin-checco-zalone-international-box-office-results-1201675349/|archive-date=2016-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在巴黎，影片共卖出价值410万的票，仅次于2007年卖出632万票的《[[蜘蛛侠3|蜘蛛侠3]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/france-box-office-star-wars-849346|title=France Box Office: 'Star Wars' Soars In Paris on Opening Day|author=Rhonda Richford|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2015-12-16|accessdate=2015-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220144408/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/france-box-office-star-wars-849346|archive-date=2015-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片于2015年11月6日在美国和加拿大上映，首周在3927张银幕上放映，是发行规模最大的邦德电影，票房预计为7000-7500万<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-second-best-james-bond-opening-peanuts-movie-weekend-box-office-preview-1201604894/ |title=''Spectre'' Poised To Be Second-Best Bond Opening Of All-Time; ''Peanuts'' Coming On Strong – Box Office Preview |publisher=deadline.com |access-date=2016-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104232050/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-second-best-james-bond-opening-peanuts-movie-weekend-box-office-preview-1201604894/ |archive-date=2015-11-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，首周四晚点映和首映日入账525万和2800万后，周末票房预计提高到7500-8000万。影片首周末票房7040万（包括IMAX点映，比前作的9600万少约2000万），但仍然在票房榜位列榜首<ref name="deadline">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-the-peanuts-movie-james-bond-box-office-1201610575/|2=|title='Spectre' $70.4M Opening: Still 2nd Highest 007 Debut Behind 'Skyfall', But Not That Far From 'Quantum Of Solace' – Monday AM|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-09|accessdate=2015-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107115522/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-the-peanuts-movie-james-bond-box-office-1201610575/|archive-date=2015-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。IMAX版在374张银幕上映，收益910万美元，超大格式版在429张银幕放映，收益800万，占首映总票房11%，意味着影片首周末在大银幕影院入账1710万（占总23%）。Cinemark XD版在112家XD影院放映，收益185万<ref name="deadline"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/11/08/spectre-box-office-007-scores-70m-for-second-best-james-bond-debut-weekend-ever/|title='Spectre' Box Office: 007 Scores $70M For Second-Best James Bond Debut Weekend Ever|author=Scott Mendelson|work=Forbes|date=2015-11-08|accessdate=2015-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151112104519/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/11/08/spectre-box-office-007-scores-70m-for-second-best-james-bond-debut-weekend-ever/|archive-date=2015-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片于11月12日在中国上映，包括午夜提前放映的79万，首映入账1500万，是单日票房第二高的好莱坞2D电影，仅次于首映1850万的《[[碟中谍5：神秘国度|碟中谍5：神秘国度]]》，占据43%的银幕<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/11/13/spectre-box-office-007-snags-15m-opening-day-in-china-will-cross-100m-us-today/|title='Spectre' Box Office: 007 Snags $15M Opening Day In China, Will Cross $100M In The U.S. Today|author=Scott Mendelson|work=Forbes|date=2015-11-13|accessdate=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://archive.is/20151127232142/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2015/11/13/spectre-box-office-007-snags-15m-opening-day-in-china-will-cross-100m-us-today/|archive-date=2015-11-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首周末影片在14700块银幕上映，票房4810万，领先前作98%<ref name="Overseas15thOpening"/>，创下好莱坞2D电影开画新纪录<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4122&p=.htm|title='Spectre' Stays at #1 as It Nears $550 Million Worldwide|author=Brad Brevet|work=Box Office Mojo|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117015923/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4122&p=.htm|archive-date=2015-11-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。IMAX版在246块银幕放映，入账460万美元，也创下11月发行电影上映前三日新纪录（超越《[[星际穿越|星际穿越]]》）<ref name="Overseas15thOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-prem-ratan-dhan-payo-martian-peanuts-paris-attacks-international-box-office-results-1201624317/|title='Spectre' Adds $152.6M In Overseas Hat Trick – International Box Office Update|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2015-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151116030638/http://deadline.com/2015/11/spectre-prem-ratan-dhan-payo-martian-peanuts-paris-attacks-international-box-office-results-1201624317/|archive-date=2015-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次周末影片票房新增1210万，环比严重下降75%，是2015年次周末下降第二严重的中国上映主流好莱坞电影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-taiwans-our-times-overcomes-flame-wars-vanquishes-hunger-games/|title=On Screen China: Taiwan's 'Our Times' Overcomes Flame Wars, Vanquishes 'Hunger Games'|author=Jonathan Papish|work=China Film Insider|date=2015-11-23|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126122914/http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-taiwans-our-times-overcomes-flame-wars-vanquishes-hunger-games/|archive-date=2015-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。四个星期总票房8470万美元（外国影片在中国只能上映30天，除非获得特批的延期）<ref name="Overseas21stOpening">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-mojin-dilwale-good-dinosaur-spectre-international-box-office-results-1201670198/|title='Star Wars' Rules Galaxy; What Else Is Up At The International Box Office|author=Nancy Tartaglione|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-12-20|accessdate=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221084630/https://deadline.com/2015/12/star-wars-mojin-dilwale-good-dinosaur-spectre-international-box-office-results-1201670198/|archive-date=2015-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管开画强势，影片还是没能获得预测的1亿的票房大关，原因主要是当地的影评人和观众评价褒贬不一和本地影片的竞争<ref name="Overseas17thOpening"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-the-martian-warms-up-a-frosty-month-for-hollywood-imports/|title=On Screen China: 'The Martian' Warms Up a Frosty Month for Hollywood Imports|author=Jonathan Papish|work=China Film Insider|date=2015-11-30|accessdate=2015-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208035752/http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-the-martian-warms-up-a-frosty-month-for-hollywood-imports/|archive-date=2015-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-taiwans-our-times-overcomes-flame-wars-vanquishes-hunger-games/|title=On Screen China: Taiwan's 'Our Times' Overcomes Flame Wars, Vanquishes 'Hunger Games'|author=Jonathan Papish|work=China Film Insider|date=2015-11-23|accessdate=2015-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126122914/http://chinafilminsider.com/on-screen-china-taiwans-our-times-overcomes-flame-wars-vanquishes-hunger-games/|archive-date=2015-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

台灣方面，首週四天票房為新台幣7812萬元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151113/36897237 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-11-13 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213115214/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151113/36897237 |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為007系列電影在台最高開片票房紀錄<ref>{{cite news |author1=王靖怡 |title=007惡魔四伏冠全台 首週創系列新高 |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201511090388.aspx |accessdate=2019-02-13 |work=[[中央社|中央社]] |date=2015-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213064209/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/201511090388.aspx |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；次週票房累計至新台幣1.4億元<ref>{{cite news |title=周末全台票房排行榜 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151120/36909300 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-11-20 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213221211/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151120/36909300 |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；第三週票房累計至新台幣1.6億元<ref>{{cite news |author1=楊景婷 |title=《紅衣小女孩》作亂台灣 許瑋甯滾血尬魔神仔 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151127/36921875/ |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-11-27 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213115214/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151127/36921875/ |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；第四週票房累計至新台幣1.76億元<ref>{{cite news |author1=謝宛儒 |title=強檔新片：雷神索爾《白鯨傳奇》漂流90天 怒海求生不成人形 |url=https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151204/36935121 |work=[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] |date=2015-12-04 |access-date=2019-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213115214/https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20151204/36935121 |archive-date=2019-02-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

